DSC Demonstration application
================================

This document gives an overview of the code structuring within the DSC demonstration platform.

app_dsc_demo			- application specific code
	\src				- source code
		dsc_config.h	- main configuration header file
		main.xc			- entry point and port definitions for application
		\motor			- contains the control loop code for outer (speed) control loop and the inner (current) control loop
		\utilities		- contains the code for the watchdog triggering code
		
module_can				- CAN interface module
module_dsc_adc			- DSC ADC interface module
module_dsc_blocks		- DSC calculation blocks (PID, Park, Clarke, Inv. Park, Inv. Clarke)
module_dsc_comms 		- CAN and Ethernet application layer
module_dsc_display 		- Shared IO interface for display, CAN enable, Ethernet enable, buttons and LEDs
module_dsc_hall 		- Hall sensor interface
module_dsc_logging 		- SDRAM / Ethernet logging interface 
module_dsc_pwm 			- PWM interface
module_dsc_sdram 		- SDRAM interface

To build the software, in the top directory of the package run:

	$ xmake all

